data.description:
Welcome Home! This contemporary townhome with nine foot ceilings on main and vaulted ceiling upper level bedrooms less than a mile from right rail station; 1 carport and 1 parking space; main level offers a large living area, kitchen with center island & pantry, generous dining area and half bathroom; upper level offers a vaulted master bedroom with full bathroom, vaulted second bedroom, laundry closet & second full bathroom on hallway. All appliances included (as well as washer & dryer). Convenient to restaurants, shopping, Rotella Park & Platte River Trails; Easy access to I-25 & I-76 and light rail transportation. Come make this your own!

*Back on market at no fault to seller, buyers loan was not accepted. 
Priced to sell, this home will not last long! Reach out for a private showing or any questions. 

Jessica Arguello 
720-514-3897
